@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_hsxzsm(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = tmp
    v0 = (((v0 + 0.88 + v0 + 0.38) - (tmp + 0.24 / tmp + 0.47)) / ((v2 + 0.13 * v2 + 0.27) + v2))
    tmp = (wp.abs(v2) - wp.sin(wp.cos(v2 + 0.96)))
    tmp = v0
    data[tid] = v0
